data.description: Escape the ordinary and embrace the good life in this 4/2 bath ranch home on peaceful Lake Waynoka, This idyllic retreat, is hugged by mature shade trees, that offer privacy and gentle breezes on those hot Summer days. With its captivating lake views, cheerful ambiance, and turnkey accessibility, this property wont last long. Get it before its gone!
